description:
In this video, I'm sharing "We Three Kings" karaoke with lyrics! This classic Christmas song is perfect for a fun karaoke night with your friends.

If you're looking for a fun and festive Christmas playlist, be sure to check out this song! The melody is easy to remember and the lyrics are sure to get everyone smiling. Plus, the key is F/Dm, so you'll be able to sing along with the ease of a pro!
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters  youtube production!
